\"ngram\": \"the aim\", \"from\": 3256, \"to\": 3263}, {\"ngram\": \"the beds\", \"from\": 3267, \"to\": 3275}, {\"ngram\": \"TODAY\", \"from\": 3349, \"to\": 3354}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, the sustainability underpinning the beds has not stopped some athletes from vocalizing certain comfort-related qualms.\", \"from\": 3358, \"to\": 3483, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sustainability\", \"from\": 3365, \"to\": 3383}, {\"ngram\": \"the beds\", \"from\": 3397, \"to\": 3405}, {\"ngram\": \"some athletes\", \"from\": 3422, \"to\": 3435}, {\"ngram\": \"certain comfort-related qualms\", \"from\": 3452, \"to\": 3482}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aleah Finnegan, a Filipino-American gymnast representing the Phillippines, shared ina TikTokthat her bed was \\\"not very soft.\\\"\", \"from\": 3484, \"to\": 3609, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3484, \"end\": 3498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aleah_Finnegan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aleah Finnegan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aleah_Finnegan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aleah_Finnegan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a Filipino-American gymnast\", \"from\": 3500, \"to\": 3527}, {\"ngram\": \"the Phillippines\", \"from\": 3541, \"to\": 3557}, {\"ngram\": \"TikTokthat\", \"from\": 3570, \"to\": 3580}, {\"ngram\": \"her bed\", \"from\": 3581, \"to\": 3588}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are not that comfortable,\\\" she concluded.\", \"from\": 3611, \"to\": 3658, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In aseparate TikTok,Australian water polo player Tilly Kearns stated that the mattress was \\\"rock hard.\\\"\", \"from\": 3660, \"to\": 3763, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3673, \"end\": 3679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.694696578160364e-49, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}, {\"begin\": 3715, \"end\": 3721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phil_Kearns\", \"score\": 0.9999944805574595, \"rank\": 5.5194654126258444e-06, \"text\": \"Kearns\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phil_Kearns\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phil_Kearns\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the mattress\", \"from\": 3734, \"to\": 3746}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A spokesperson from Airweave, the company that makes the mattresses, told TODAY, \\\"Airweave differs from traditional mattresses by containing no springs or foam - we have collaborated with sleep experts and athletes to optimize the performance-enhancing benefits of sleeping on an airweave mattress.\", \"from\": 3765, \"to\": 4063, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A spokesperson\", \"from\": 3765, \"to\": 3779}, {\"ngram\": \"Airweave\", \"from\": 3785, \"to\": 3793}, {\"ngram\": \"the company\", \"from\": 3795, \"to\": 3806}, {\"ngram\": \"the mattresses\", \"from\": 3818, \"to\": 3832}, {\"ngram\": \"TODAY\", \"from\": 3839, \"to\": 3844}, {\"ngram\": \"Airweave differs\", \"from\": 3847, \"to\": 3863}, {\"ngram\": \"traditional mattresses\", \"from\": 3869, \"to\": 3891}, {\"ngram\": \"no springs\", \"from\": 3906, \"to\": 3916}, {\"ngram\": \"foam\", \"from\": 3920, \"to\": 3924}, {\"ngram\": \"sleep experts\", \"from\": 3953, \"to\": 3966}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 3971, \"to\": 3979}, {\"ngram\": \"the performance-enhancing benefits\", \"from\": 3992, \"to\": 4026}, {\"ngram\": \"an airweave mattress\", \"from\": 4042, \"to\": 4062}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We encourage all athletes to join us at the Mattress Fitting Center in Athletes Village for a personalized consultation, which uses our AI-based MattressFit app to analyze and recommend the best configuration for their body type/needs.\", \"from\": 4065, \"